For example:
üí°
Happy Tiger Dances In Bright Daylight.  
Each letter in the mnemonic represents the first letter of an important HTML tag or element:
H: <h1> (Heading 1)
T: <title> (Document Title)
D: <div> (Division)
I: <img> (Image)
B: <button> (Button)
a: <a> (Anchor/Link)
